title: The Legend of Chinese Zodiac
overview: Xing Hu was an orphan and he was brought up by a tigress. After Shen Nung's revealing, Xing Hu took the emperorship which called "The twelve medical folk". He started to look for the 12 zodiac animals with Shen Nung's apprentice--- Xue Lian, together and they hoped they could save the world.
